, tsingy habitat at the western margin of the 
<location id="8EEFDFE5FFFA0F5EF6B8F3DEC66DF321" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03993828FFFA0F5FFAF3F4D6C8ADFB70:8EEFDFE5FFFA0F5EF6B8F3DEC66DF321" box="[2344,2584,3169,3202]" municipality="Antsalova District" name="Bemaraha Massif" pageId="8" pageNumber="191" stateProvince="Melaky Region">Bemaraha Massif</location>
and east of 
<location id="8EEFDFE5FFFA0F5EF990F338CAFCF30B" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03993828FFFA0F5FFAF3F4D6C8ADFB70:8EEFDFE5FFFA0F5EF990F338CAFCF30B" box="[1536,1673,3207,3240]" municipality="Antsalova District" name="Antsalova" pageId="8" pageNumber="191" stateProvince="Melaky Region">Antsalova</location>
